Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants where it appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + Resolved compared to when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait in cases that eventually execute Completed + In Call versus cases that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities occur consecutively or with intermediate steps
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between the start of Accepted + Wait and the start of Completed + In Call within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait grouped by country to assess regional differences in waiting behavior before potential escalation to Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait in variants containing Queued + Awaiting Assignment prior to Accepted + Wait, compared to variants without such queuing
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Time of Accepted + Wait in process executions that transition directly to Completed + In Call without intermediate resolution steps
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Cycle Time of Accepted + Wait when it occurs after Accepted + In Progress and before Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time between Accepted + Wait and Completed + Resolved versus between Accepted + Wait and Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in high-frequency variants (e.g., top 5 most frequent) that lead to different terminal activities including Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of Accepted + Wait in variants where Completed + In Call appears as an intermediate activity before final closure
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time from the preceding Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait, and then from Accepted + Wait to Completed + In Call, measured separately to isolate waiting impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time of Accepted + Wait in cases handled by different org:group units that later perform Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:group filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call'
